                "type": "paragraph",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "The scheme \"Indira Gandhi National Old Age Pension Scheme\" is implemented by the Social Welfare Department, Government of Chhattisgarh. Under this scheme, financial assistance is provided to elderly people aged 60 years and above living Below the Poverty Line (BPL) to support them in living a respectful life. This scheme is centrally sponsored."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
