          "process_md": "&gt; **Registration Process:**\n\n**Step 1:** Go to the [eDistrict Chhattisgarh Portal](https://edistrict.cgstate.gov.in/PACE/login.do#login).\n**Step 2:** Click on &amp;quot;[Citizen Login](https://edistrict.cgstate.gov.in/PACE/newCitizenLogin.do?OWASP_CSRFTOKEN=FHE7-J58X-CSIV-ZT6W-D8B6-OQ33-7RMQ-YCBE)&amp;quot;.\n**Step 3:** If you are a new user, select &amp;quot;[New Registration](https://edistrict.cgstate.gov.in/PACE/CitizenLogin.do?OWASP_CSRFTOKEN=FHE7-J58X-CSIV-ZT6W-D8B6-OQ33-7RMQ-YCBE)&amp;quot;.\n**Step 4:** Enter your registration details and click &amp;quot;Submit&amp;quot;.\n**Step 5:** Your Registration Summary will be displayed, and you will receive your password on your registered mobile number.\n&gt; **Application Process:**\n\n**Step 1:** Go to the [eDistrict Chhattisgarh Portal](https://edistrict.cgstate.gov.in/PACE/login.do#login).\n**Step 2:** Click on ‘Login’ or &amp;quot;[Citizen Login](https://edistrict.cgstate.gov.in/PACE/newCitizenLogin.do?OWASP_CSRFTOKEN=FHE7-J58X-CSIV-ZT6W-D8B6-OQ33-7RMQ-YCBE)&amp;quot;.\n**Step 3:** Enter your username and password and click ‘Login’.\n**Step 4:** After logging in, click on &amp;quot;My Service&amp;quot; and search for the scheme to apply for.\n**Step 5:** Click on ‘Apply Online’ and fill in all required details, upload important documents, and click ‘Submit.’\n"
        },
        {
