        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n   1. The applicant should be a native of Chhattisgarh.\n   1. The applicant should be a senior citizen.\n   1. The applicant should be 60 years of age or older.\n   1. The applicant&amp;#39;s name should be included in the list of families living Below Poverty Line.\n   1. The applicant should not be receiving pension benefits from any other Central or State Government pension scheme.\n\n",
